snippet.title: socialprotection.org
snippet.description:
socialprotection.org is a centralised platform by which to access the most up-to-date, comprehensive database and multimedia learning materials on social protection. It aims to facilitate knowledge sharing and capacity building on effective social protection policies and programmes by fostering an online community of social protection practitioners.

In this YouTube channel you will find our latest webinars – uploaded as soon as they happened –, livestreamed events and other videos of interest to policy makers, experts and students.  

socialprotection.org is an unbranded and member-based platform. Learn more about us and become a member – it’s free: http://bit.ly/2y4MTY8

Join our mailing list to be updated on future webinars and events: http://bit.ly/2ygHEBN
